The Europeans decided to humiliate the Russians, and immediately went from the main trump card - from the Dutchman. He akimbo and proudly - "We have the best attitude towards faggots in the Netherlands - and marriages are allowed, and parades are easy!" The Russian grunted: "And you, dear man, look at our latest laws." The Dutchman looked, his face turned pale. “Yes,” he says, embarrassed, “ours, of course, have both marriages and parades, but so that the majority in the government ...”